			<p> Dusty Paws is a small start-up created by five aspiring studnets who want to make a change in the world, one paw at a time! </p>

			<h2> 1.2 Our Mission </h2>
			<p>We want to simplify the method of owning a pet and caring for the pet by making thr whole process available on one site! Who wouldn't love being able to make a new best firend, as well as being prepared to introduce them to their new home. </p>

			<h2> 1.3 Our Vision </h2>
			<p>5 years from now, Dusty Paws aims to be able to supply pet essentials for all species, from cat litter to snake food.  </p>

			<h1>Policies</h1>
			<h2> 2.1 Privacy </h2>
			<p>Dusty paws respects your privacy does not intend to betray your trust, just like how you should never betray an animal! Any personal data that is gathered, will stay within the pack and would never make its way to any outsiders.We promise to use any personal data responsibly and take great care when handling it. </p>

