			<p>We collect essential data such as you username, to ensure that only authorised users can have access to being able to reserve a pet, create a blog, or purchase any items. This collected when a user is logged in. </p>

			<h2> 2.3 Who's data we collect </h2>
			<p>Anyone who registered an account with Dusty Paws, will automatically be accepting cookies used to optimise their experience on the site.</p>

			<h2> 2.4 UK Data Protection Act 2018 <strong>(GDPR 2018)</strong> </h2>
			<p>The data taken from your time on Dusty Paws, will NEVER be used in vain nor will it be used to put you and your new friend in harms way. For more information about GDPR 2018, go to <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/guide-to-the-general-data-protection-regulation">Guide to the General Data Protection Regulation</a> </p>

